section1.text1: I train karate, which shows my determination, discipline. I work as a nurse, which shows my commitment to helping others, empathy and ability to handle stressful situations. I study computer science, which reflects my curiosity, my desire to explore new technologies. The combination of these three areas makes me a well-rounded person, ready for both physical and intellectual challenges.
